### Test Server
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### User Signup
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "Test@123",
    "phone": "03123456789",
    "cnic": "1234512345678",
    "address": "Karachi, Pakistan"
}

### User Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "Test@123"
}

### Admin Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@attendly.com",
    "password": "Admin@123"
}

### Get User Profile (after login, use token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Check In
POST http://localhost:5000/api/attendance/checkin
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "latitude": 24.8607,
    "longitude": 67.0011,
    "location_name": "Office"
}

### Check Out
POST http://localhost:5000/api/attendance/checkout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "latitude": 24.8607,
    "longitude": 67.0011,
    "location_name": "Office"
}

### Get Today's Status
GET http://localhost:5000/api/attendance/today
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get User Reports
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/reports?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE